      <title>前首相抨击苏纳克的财政记录 保守党仍受特拉斯阴影笼罩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/truss-shadow-still-hangs-over-tories-as-ex-pm-slams-sunak-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[利兹·特拉斯表示，她在英国大选中的表现会比里希·苏纳克更好，并拒绝支持任何四位试图接替苏纳克的保守党候选人，这一政治干预凸显了这位任职 49 天的前首相在保守党中仍然拥有重要影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/truss-shadow-still-hangs-over-tories-as-ex-pm-slams-sunak-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 13:40:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿万富翁的现金热潮有望推翻民主党的关键参议员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/montana-senate-rush-of-billionaire-cash-poised-to-topple-democrat-jon-tester</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔恩·泰斯特对激烈的政治斗争并不陌生。作为来自蒙大拿州的民主党参议员，他已经连任三届，这自然是理所当然的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/montana-senate-rush-of-billionaire-cash-poised-to-topple-democrat-jon-tester</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 13:00:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平在刺激计划发布后的首次讲话中警告未来面临障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/xi-warns-of-obstacles-ahead-in-first-speech-after-stimulus-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是中国政府宣布史无前例的经济刺激计划以来，国家主席习近平首次公开发表讲话，呼吁人们谨慎应对中国未来可能面临的困难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/xi-warns-of-obstacles-ahead-in-first-speech-after-stimulus-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 12:17:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利比亚议会通过央行行长投票为恢复石油供应铺平道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/libya-assembly-paves-way-to-oil-restart-with-central-banker-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[利比亚东部议会批准了新任央行行长，结束了围绕该欧佩克成员国巨额能源收入控制权的僵局，为全面恢复石油生产奠定了基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/libya-assembly-paves-way-to-oil-restart-with-central-banker-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 11:03:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国外长就向乌克兰提供巡航导弹问题发表不同意见</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/german-minister-breaks-ranks-on-long-range-missiles-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国外交部长安娜莱娜·贝尔博克表示支持乌克兰要求获得远程金牛座巡航导弹的请求，这与德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨的观点相左，后者已排除向乌克兰运送此类武器的可能性，因为担心这可能引发与俄罗斯的直接冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/german-minister-breaks-ranks-on-long-range-missiles-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 09:10:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>玛丽娜·勒庞因涉嫌滥用欧盟资金在巴黎接受审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/marine-le-pen-faces-paris-trial-over-allegations-of-misuse-of-eu-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统候选人玛丽娜·勒庞表示，她不会在巴黎审判首日逃避任何问题。她和她所在的国民联盟党被指控挪用数百万欧元的欧盟资金在法国搭建竞选平台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/marine-le-pen-faces-paris-trial-over-allegations-of-misuse-of-eu-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 08:35:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳斯鲁拉死后，以色列袭击贝鲁特，袭击升级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/israel-hits-central-beirut-as-raids-widen-after-nasrallah-death</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在与黎巴嫩真主党交战近一年后，以色列首次对贝鲁特市中心进行了轰炸。自上周伊朗支持的该组织头目被杀后，以色列加强了空袭力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/israel-hits-central-beirut-as-raids-widen-after-nasrallah-death</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 08:25:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非经济出现转机 债券收益率跌至两年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/south-africa-s-deputy-president-sees-growth-accelerating-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着南非副总统增强人们对非洲大陆最大经济体正在扭转局面的信心，南非基准债券收益率两年多来首次跌破 10%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/south-africa-s-deputy-president-sees-growth-accelerating-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 08:20:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国放弃 2024 年实现增长的希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/germany-is-giving-up-hope-of-achieving-any-growth-at-all-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，德国政府准备下调对欧洲最大经济体的预测，目前预计今年德国经济将完全不会扩张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/germany-is-giving-up-hope-of-achieving-any-growth-at-all-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 08:14:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
